(9, 1, '2015-02-02 04:30:57', '2015-02-02 04:30:57', '[vc_row rt_row_background_width="default" rt_row_content_width="fullwidth" rt_row_style="default-style" rt_row_borders="" rt_overlap="" rt_grid="" rt_row_paddings="false" rt_bg_effect="classic" rt_bg_parallax_effect="1" rt_bg_image_repeat="repeat" rt_bg_size="cover" rt_bg_position="right top" rt_bg_attachment="scroll"][vc_column width="1/1"][rev_slider_vc alias="ss_about"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row rt_row_background_width="default" rt_row_content_width="default" rt_row_style="default-style" rt_overlap="true" rt_row_paddings="true" rt_bg_effect="classic" rt_bg_parallax_effect="1" rt_bg_image_repeat="repeat" rt_bg_size="cover" rt_bg_position="right top" rt_bg_attachment="scroll" rt_row_borders="bottom" rt_grid="" class="txt-justify"][vc_column width="1/1"][rt_heading style="style-1" size="h1"]About Us[/rt_heading][vc_column_text]<span style="font-weight: 100;">DanielHart &amp; Dayo LLP is the Nigerian law firm for corporate citizens. We advise clients on a focused range of legal matters, with a rich appreciation of the applicable laws and litigation strategies in Nigeria. We are also proud of our commercial acumen and marketplace insights. Our clients are offered advice to strengthen their market competitiveness, mitigate risks and navigate potential market disruptions.  </span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 100;">What makes us different is our commitment to creating corporate citizens in Nigeria. To compliment our legal and commercial advice, we provide insights that guide investors operating in Nigeria toward responsible business initiatives. We develop strategies for our clients to build trust-creating partnerships with agents of government, other businesses and civil society.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 100;">Our three dimensional approach—combining legal, commercial and corporate citizenship advice—is what really makes us a full service law firm. </span><span style="font-weight: 100;">We believe doing-well and doing-good will truly optimize the position of our clients on legal, financial and social fronts in Nigeria. Accordingly, our distinct strategies also highlight investment opportunities that will enhance our clients’ social impact—and in the process—their social license. We are intentionally holistic, working smarter to solve our client’s legal problems and helping to prevent some too! DanielHart &amp; Dayo LLP is the pioneer Nigerian law firm specializing in corporate citizenship advisory services.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row rt_row_background_width="default" rt_row_content_width="default" rt_row_style="default-style" rt_row_paddings="true" rt_bg_effect="classic" rt_bg_parallax_effect="1" rt_bg_image_repeat="repeat" rt_bg_size="cover" rt_bg_position="right top" rt_bg_attachment="scroll" rt_grid="true" rt_row_borders="" rt_overlap="" class="txt-justify"][vc_column width="1/2"][rt_heading style="style-1" size="h4"]Our Philosophy[/rt_heading][vc_column_text]In today’s economy, success is largely defined by your company’s ability to turn an idea into value—faster than the competition.\r\n\r\nWe want to help you achieve that success, and we know the way we do so is important to you.\r\n\r\nWe believe our principles will enrich your experience with us as we work towards your success:[/vc_column_text][vc_accordion style="icons" first_one_open="" class="philosophy-accordion"][vc_accordion_tab title="Be trusted" icon_name="icon-ok"][vc_column_text]<span style="font-weight: 400;">We understand T.R.U.S.T as five very demanding letters—that also represent rights you deserve as clients:</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">   </span> <span style="font-weight: 400;">Taking on your concerns.</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">   </span> <span style="font-weight: 400;">Respecting they are confidential.</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">   </span> <span style="font-weight: 400;">Understanding who you are in the process.</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">   </span> <span style="font-weight: 400;">Staying sensitive to our role in your growth and success.</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">  Telling you our honest opinion and ensuring it adds value.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Legally, Section 19 of the Nigerian Rules of Professional Conduct for Legal Practitioners (2007) gives you—our client—the right to confidentiality and privilege. We know what trust means to you. With these five steps, we go beyond the legal requirements to provide a rare level of reliability and trust.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Be better than expected" icon_name="icon-ok"][vc_column_text]<span style="font-weight: 400;">Expectations. Everybody has them—and rightfully so! We think about your expectations. The extra mile is hard to define. But you know when it’s been accomplished. You can recognize the lawyer who always finds a solution and does not settle for the easy answer or option. It is about work ethic and an unwavering commitment to results. It is about positive energy. At our firm, we never say, “it can’t be done”. We know you have high expectations, so we treat every client like one in a million, not one of a million. For partnering with us, we are proud to go above and beyond for you, everyday.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Be thoughtful" icon_name="icon-ok"][vc_column_text]<span style="font-weight: 400;">Your brief is constantly on our mind and you will know that it is! This is one of our distinctive features. We do not believe clients should have to follow-up with their lawyers—chasing for answers to an enquiry or having to ask for a status update. We will work on your case diligently and provide you with weekly updates on the progress being made. We will anticipate matters you may not have, and bring them to your attention. We believe “the details” are hidden with treasures that add value to your business and experience with us—so we fixate on them.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Be professional" icon_name="icon-ok"][vc_column_text]<span style="font-weight: 400;">It underscores everything we do. How we engage with you. How we represent you. How we conduct ourselves. Our delivery. And the outcome. Professionalism is the signature hallmark in our DNA—it identifies and separates us. Our firm’s logo is a promise of quality. We apply this to everything from our written submissions and court engagements to our daily operations.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">In our daily operations, we are also obsessive about organization. We apply that obsession to every file, document and matter regarding your brief. We also appreciate the difference between organization and planning. Organization is about creating order systems in every area. Accordingly, we maintain systems and structures that keep your brief in meticulous order. Planning is about using that level of organization to ensure your experience runs smoothly—from project inception to completion. We anticipate your project’s life cycle and contingencies. We make detailed plans and arrangements to advance progress along the way. At our firm, we organize and plan—so you can rest at ease.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Be cultured" icon_name="icon-ok"][vc_column_text]<span style="font-weight: 400;">In an age of fast-paced lifestyles and on-the-go technology, we are proud to be old school about etiquette. We consider it a timeless virtue. Our attention to courtesy and politeness helps deliver the elegant interaction you deserve. It’s also the reason why we reply your emails in a wholesome and timely fashion—even if it is just a message to acknowledge we have heard you, and inform you a more lengthy response is on its way. We are steeped in cultural traditions about simple manners and you will notice we apply them to all our dealings with you—and even between the partners! Your traditions are also important to us, so we will do our homework and operate with the savoir-faire expected in your culture.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Be “glocal”" icon_name="icon-ok"][vc_column_text]<span style="font-weight: 400;">Exceptional legal advice is just a start. We think about your business on local and global frontiers. Our brand is a commitment to the gold standard—on both fronts. Choosing to partner with our brand means you feel confident about attaining the gold standard of responsible business on the local front. We are also sensitive to your business needs to succeed internationally. We have created a global network of lawyers ready to represent you in strategic markets and fast-growing economies.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][/vc_accordion][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][rt_heading style="style-1" size="h4"]Our Clients[/rt_heading][vc_column_text]Our primary clients are foreign investors and companies seeking to enter the Nigerian market place. Our partners have worked in London, California, Switzerland as well as in Lagos and Port Harcourt. We were educated at prestigious universities in the United Kingdom and the United States of America, obtaining advanced degrees in subject matters ranging from international law to financial law.\r\n\r\nWe understand the DNA of a wide range of clients and have one partner with a U.S. MBA perspective. Collectively, we have been on the inside of Nigerian law firms, a foreign law firm, Nigerian banks, international NGOs, technology firms in California, government ministries, a PPP real estate firm and an international institution. Together, we speak different languages and have 10 years experience—spanning the public and private sectors. We draw on our world-class abilities and international experiences to ensure our clients always receive the white glove treatment.\r\n\r\nWe also proudly represent Nigerian clients on a focused range of legal briefs. We strive to consistently deliver the highest standard and quality of legal service that operates in tandem with the proficient, older-generation law firm in Nigeria. By combining this level of service with our new-era mindset and creative application of the laws, we are uniquely informed to guide and represent your business—in a new era of stakeholder economics.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row rt_row_background_width="default" rt_row_content_width="default" rt_row_style="alt-style-1" rt_row_paddings="true" rt_bg_effect="classic" rt_bg_parallax_effect="1" rt_bg_image_repeat="repeat" rt_bg_size="cover" rt_bg_position="right top" rt_bg_attachment="scroll" rt_padding_top="60" rt_padding_bottom="60"][vc_column width="1/1"][rt_heading size="h3" style="style-4" punchline="Our Team"]Who''s behind the scenes?[/rt_heading][staff_box list_layout="1/2" list_orderby="date" list_order="DESC" ids="1872,1871"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row rt_row_background_width="default" rt_row_content_width="default" rt_row_style="light-style" rt_row_paddings="true" rt_bg_effect="classic" rt_bg_parallax_effect="3" rt_bg_image_repeat="no-repeat" rt_bg_size="cover" rt_bg_position="right top" rt_bg_attachment="scroll" rt_grid="true" rt_padding_top="100" rt_padding_bottom="140" rt_row_borders="" rt_overlap="" rt_bg_color="rgba(3,19,28,0.13)"][vc_column width="1/4"][rt_counter number="174"]Web Design Projects[/rt_counter][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/4"][rt_counter number="299"]Video Productions[/rt_counter][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/4"][rt_counter number="150"]Animations[/rt_counter][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/4"][rt_counter number="1100"]Graphic Designs[/rt_counter][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row rt_row_background_width="default" rt_row_content_width="default" rt_row_style="default-style" rt_overlap="" rt_row_paddings="true" rt_bg_effect="classic" rt_bg_parallax_effect="1" rt_bg_image_repeat="no-repeat" rt_bg_size="cover" rt_bg_position="right top" rt_bg_attachment="fixed" rt_row_borders="top,bottom" rt_grid="" rt_padding_top="60" rt_padding_bottom="60"][vc_column width="1/1"][rt_heading style="style-4" size="h4"]Our Story[/rt_heading][rt_timeline id=""][rt_tl_event month="December," year="2012"]<span style="font-weight: 400;">After attending SOAS together (from 2005-2006) and maintaining a strong connection for six years, Hart and Daniel convene at Cafe Nero, Regent Street, London. Hart had already been admitted to the Nigerian bar in 2008. They discuss Hart’s involvement in the firm. Hart goes home to pray on the decision, and then confirms interest weeks later.</span>[/rt_tl_event][rt_tl_event year="2013/2014"]<span style="font-weight: 400;">Collectively, we refined our firm’s strategy and value proposition, having mapped our business opportunities and competitive advantages. Our structural and operational foundations were in place by Q4 of 2014.  Accordingly, we embarked on the processes to formally incorporate the firm under section 659 of the Nigerian Companies and Allied Matters Act (1990).</span>[/rt_tl_event][rt_tl_event month="March," year="2015"]<span style="font-weight: 400;">The Corporate Affairs Commission (CAC) of Nigeria incorporates the firm as a legal entity. DanielHart &amp; Dayo LLP is listed in the CAC’s register of business names, and certified as a “legal practice and consultancy” with the following certification number: BN2337967.</span>[/rt_tl_event][rt_tl_event month="March," year="2015"]<span style="font-weight: 400;">Client enquires are being answered.</span>[/rt_tl_event][/rt_timeline][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row rt_row_background_width="default" rt_row_content_width="default" rt_row_style="alt-style-2" rt_row_paddings="true" rt_bg_effect="classic" rt_bg_parallax_effect="1" rt_bg_image_repeat="repeat" rt_bg_size="cover" rt_bg_position="right top" rt_bg_attachment="scroll" rt_overlap="" rt_padding_top="60" rt_padding_bottom="60" rt_row_borders="" rt_grid=""][vc_column width="1/1"][rt_heading size="h3" style="style-4" punchline="Testimonials"]What They Are Saying[/rt_heading][testimonial_carousel list_layout="1/1" align="center" max_item="10" nav="false" dots="true" list_orderby="date" list_order="DESC" client_images="false" style="center big" ids="2353,1735"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'ABOUT US', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'about-us', '', '', '2015-11-10 17:25:38', '2015-11-10 17:25:38', '', 0, 'http://rttheme19.rtthemes.com/?page_id=9', 0, 'page', '', 0),
