(2726, 1, '2015-06-15 21:47:11', '2015-06-15 21:47:11', '[vc_row rt_row_background_width="default" rt_row_content_width="fullwidth" rt_row_style="default-style" rt_row_borders="" rt_overlap="" rt_grid="" rt_row_paddings="true" rt_bg_image="2959" rt_bg_effect="classic" rt_bg_parallax_effect="1" rt_bg_image_repeat="repeat" rt_bg_size="cover" rt_bg_position="right top" rt_bg_attachment="scroll" rt_padding_top="250" rt_padding_bottom="250"][vc_column][rt_heading style="style-1" size="h1"][/rt_heading][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row rt_row_background_width="default" rt_row_content_width="default" rt_row_style="default-style" rt_overlap="true" rt_row_paddings="true" rt_bg_effect="classic" rt_bg_parallax_effect="1" rt_bg_image_repeat="repeat" rt_bg_size="cover" rt_bg_position="right top" rt_bg_attachment="scroll" rt_row_borders="bottom" rt_grid="" class="txt-justify"][vc_column width="1/1"][rt_heading style="style-1" size="h1"]Corporate Citizenship[/rt_heading][vc_column_text]<span style="font-weight: 100;">Beyond legal and commercial advice, we create a full service suite of corporate responsibility and social engagement plans to grow your triple bottom line.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 100;">We integrate extrinsic values as well as social and environmental objectives into the management and expansion of your wealth. We offer world-class knowledge and a comprehensive range of tailored that help you create a long-lasting impact in Nigeria.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 100;">We position our clients to address environmental, economic and social challenges. Our clients become corporate citizens with measurable impact on the Nigerian economy they will be proud to report.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 100;">We achieve this through a range of and innovative solutions and options within our portfolio. We can assist clients in setting up philanthropic structures, or direct them on innovative products in impact investment and microfinance, or integrating sustainability criteria in an investment portfolio. This is a short-list of our citizenship portfolio options. We assist you in the choice of the best strategy to meet your particular objectives and turn your vision into reality – based on your convictions, ideals and economic ability.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 100;">To you sustain your corporate citizenship portfolio, we provide information on events, the latest research publications, as well as a network of thematic experts and strategic partner organizations to compliment your business objectives.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Being a Corporate Citizen', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'being-a-corporate-citizen', '', '', '2015-10-17 21:21:08', '2015-10-17 21:21:08', '', 0, 'http://www.danielhartdayo.com/?page_id=2726', 0, 'page', '', 0),
