cooking—with a particular appreciation of Nigerian cuisine. </span>\r\n\r\n<b>Languages</b>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">English (Mother tongue) Igbo (Basic)</span>', 'Sofiri Ezekiel-Hart', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1871-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-01 20:49:18', '2015-09-01 20:49:18', '', 1871, 'http://www.danielhartdayo.com/2015/09/01/1871-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
