ole in your growth and success.</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">   </span> <span style="font-weight: 400;">Telling you our honest opinion and ensuring it adds value.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Legally, Section 19 of the Nigerian Rules of Professional Conduct for Legal Practitioners (2007) gives you—our client—the right to confidentiality and privilege. We know what trust means to you. With these five steps, we go beyond the legal requirements to provide a rare level of reliability and trust.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Be better than expected" icon_name="icon-ok"][vc_column_text]<span style="font-weight: 400;">Expectations. Everybody has them—and rightfully so! We think about your expectations. The extra mile is hard to define. But you know when it’s been accomplished. You can recognize the lawyer who always finds a solution and does not settle for the easy answer or option. It is about work ethic and an unwavering commitment to results. It is about positive energy. At our firm, we never say, “it can’t be done”. We know you have high expectations, so we treat every client like one in a million, not one of a million. For partnering with us, we are proud to go above and beyond for you, everyday.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Be thoughtful" icon_name="icon-ok"][vc_column_text]<span style="font-weight: 400;">Your brief is constantly on our mind and you will know that it is! This is one of our distinctive features. We do not believe clients should have to follow-up with their lawyers—chasing for answers to an enquiry or having to ask for a status update. We will work on your case diligently and provide you with weekly updates on the progress being made. We will anticipate matters you may not have, and bring them to your attention. We believe “the details” are hidden with treasures that add value to your business and experience with us—so we fixate 