nd even between the partners! Your traditions are also important to us, so we will do our homework and operate with the savoir-faire expected in your culture.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Be “glocal”" icon_name="icon-ok"][vc_column_text]<span style="font-weight: 400;">Exceptional legal advice is just a start. We think about your business on local and global frontiers. Our brand is a commitment to the gold standard—on both fronts. Choosing to partner with our brand means you feel confident about attaining the gold standard of responsible business on the local front. We are also sensitive to your business needs to succeed internationally. We have created a global network of lawyers ready to represent you in strategic markets and fast-growing economies.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][/vc_accordion][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][rt_heading style="style-1" size="h4"]Our Clients[/rt_heading][vc_column_text]Our primary clients are foreign investors and companies seeking to enter the Nigerian market place. Our partners have worked in London, California, Switzerland as well as in Lagos and Port Harcourt. We were educated at prestigious universities in the United Kingdom and the United States of America, obtaining advanced degrees in subject matters ranging from international law to financial law.\r\n\r\nWe understand the DNA of a wide range of clients and have one partner with a U.S. MBA perspective. Collectively, we have been on the inside of Nigerian law firms, a foreign law firm, Nigerian banks, international NGOs, technology firms in California, government ministries, a PPP real estate firm and an international institution. Together, we speak different languages and have 10 years experience—spanning the public and private sectors. We draw on our world-class abilities and international experiences to ensure our clients always receive the white glove treatment.\r\n\r\nWe also proudly represent Nigerian clients on a focused range of legal briefs. We strive to consistently deliver the highest standard and quality of legal service that operates in tandem with the proficient, older-generation law firm in Nigeria. By combining this level of service with our new-era mindset and creative application of the laws, we are uniquely informed to guide and represent your business—in a new era of stakeholder economics.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row rt_row_background_width="default" rt_row_content_width="default" rt_row_style="alt-style-1" rt_row_paddings="true" rt_bg_effect="classic" rt_bg_parallax_effect="1" rt_bg_image_repeat="repeat" rt_bg_size="cover" rt_bg_position="right top" rt_bg_attachment="scroll" rt_padding_top="60" rt_padding_bottom="60"][vc_column width="1/1"][rt_heading size="h3" style="style-4" punchline="Our Team"]Who''s behind the scenes?[/rt_heading][staff_box list_layout="1/2" list_orderby="date" list_order="DESC" ids="1872,1871"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row rt_row_background_width="default" rt_row_content_width="default" rt_row_style="light-style" rt_row_paddings="true" rt_bg_effect="classic" rt_bg_parallax_effect="3" rt_bg_image_repeat="no-repeat" rt_bg_size="cover" rt_bg_position="right top" rt_bg_attachment="scroll" rt_grid="true" rt_padding_top="100" rt_padding_bottom="140" rt_row_borders="" rt_overlap="" rt_bg_color="rgba(3,19,28,0.13)"][vc_column width="1/4"][rt_counter number="174"]Web Design Projects[/rt_counter][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/4"][rt_counter number="299"]Video Productions[/rt_counter][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/4"][rt_counter number="150"]Animations[/rt_counter][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/4"][rt_counter number="1100"]Graphic Designs[/rt_counter][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row rt_row_background_width="default" rt_row_content_width="default" rt_row_style="default-style" rt_overlap="" rt_row_paddings="true" rt_bg_effect="classic" rt_bg_parallax_effect="1" rt_bg_image_repeat="no-repeat" rt_bg_size="cover" rt_bg_position="right top" rt_bg_attachment="fixed" rt_row_borders="top,bottom" rt_grid="" rt_padding_top="60" rt_padding_bottom="60"][vc_column width="1/1"][rt_heading style="style-4" size="h4"]Our Story[/rt_heading][rt_timeline id=""][rt_tl_event month="December," year="2012"]<span style="font-weight: 400;">After attending SOAS together (from 2005-2006) and maintaining a strong connection for six years, Hart and Daniel convene at Cafe Nero, Regent Street, London. Hart had already been admitted to the Nigerian bar in 2008. They discuss Hart’s involvement in the firm. Hart goes home to pray on the decision, and then confirms interest weeks later.</span>[/rt_tl_event][rt_tl_event year="2013/2014"]<span style="font-weight: 400;">Collectively, we refined our firm’s strategy and value proposition, having mapped our business opportunities and competitive advantages. Our structural and operational foundations were in place by Q4 of 2014.  Accordingly, we embarked on the processes to formally incorporate the firm under section 659 of the Nigerian Companies and Allied Matters Act (1990).</span>[/rt_tl_event][rt_tl_event month="March," year="2015"]<span style="font-weight: 400;">The Corporate Affairs Commission (CAC) of Nigeria incorporates the firm as a legal entity. DanielHart &amp; Dayo LLP is listed in the CAC’s register of business names, and certified as a “legal practice and consultancy” with the following certification number: BN2337967.</span>[/rt_tl_event][rt_tl_event month="March," year="2015"]<span style="font-weight: 400;">Client enquires are being answered.</span>[/rt_tl_event][/rt_timeline][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row rt_row_background_width="default" rt_row_content_width="default" rt_row_style="alt-style-2" rt_row_paddings="true" rt_bg_effect="classic" rt_bg_parallax_effect="1" rt_bg_image_repeat="repeat" rt_bg_size="cover" rt_bg_position="right top" rt_bg_attachment="scroll" rt_overlap="" rt_padding_top="60" rt_padding_bottom="60" rt_row_borders="" rt_grid=""][vc_column width="1/1"][rt_