a focused range of legal briefs. We strive to consistently deliver the highest standard and quality of legal service that operates in tandem with the proficient, older-generation law firm in Nigeria. By combining this level of service with our new-era mindset and creative application of the laws, we are uniquely informed to guide and represent your business—in a new era of stakeholder economics.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row rt_row_background_width="default" rt_row_content_width="default" rt_row_style="alt-style-1" rt_row_paddings="true" rt_bg_effect="classic" rt_bg_parallax_effect="1" rt_bg_image_repeat="repeat" rt_bg_size="cover" rt_bg_position="right top" rt_bg_attachment="scroll" rt_padding_top="60" rt_padding_bottom="60"][vc_column width="1/1"][rt_heading size="h3" style="style-4" punchline="Our Team"]Who''s behind the scenes?[/rt_heading][staff_box list_layout="1/2" list_orderby="date" list_order="DESC" ids="1872,1871"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row rt_row_background_width="default" rt_row_content_width="default" rt_row_style="light-style" rt_row_paddings="true" rt_bg_effect="classic" rt_bg_parallax_effect="3" rt_bg_image_repeat="no-repeat" rt_bg_size="cover" rt_bg_position="right top" rt_bg_attachment="scroll" rt_grid="true" rt_padding_top="100" rt_padding_bottom="140" rt_row_borders="" rt_overlap="" rt_bg_color="rgba(3,19,28,0.13)"][vc_column width="1/4"][rt_counter number="174"]Web Design Projects[/rt_counter][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/4"][rt_counter number="299"]Video Productions[/rt_counter][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/4"][rt_counter number="150"]Animations[/rt_counter][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/4"][rt_counter number="1100"]Graphic Designs[/rt_counter][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row rt_row_background_width="default" rt_row_content_width="default" rt_row_style="default-style" rt_overlap="" rt_row_paddings="true" rt_bg_effect="classic" rt_bg_parallax_effect="1" rt_bg_image_repeat="no-repeat" rt_bg_size="cover" rt_bg_position="right top" rt_bg_attachment="fixed" rt_row_borders="top,bottom" rt_grid="" rt_padding_top="60" rt_padding_bottom="60"][vc_column width="1/1"][rt_heading style="style-4" size="h4"]Our Story[/rt_heading][rt_timeline id=""][rt_tl_event month="December," year="2012"]<span style="font-weight: 400;">After attending SOAS together (from 2005-2006) and maintaining a strong connection for six years, Hart and Daniel convene at Cafe Nero, Regent Street, London. Hart had already been admitted to the Nigerian bar in 2008. They discuss Hart’s involvement in the firm. Hart goes home to pray on the decision, and then confirms interest weeks later.</span>[/rt_tl_event][rt_tl_event year="2013/2014"]<span style="font-weight: 400;">Collectively, we refined our firm’s strategy and value proposition, having mapped our business opportunities and competitive advantages. Our structural and operational foundations were in place by Q4 of 2014.  Accordingly, we embarked on the processes to formally incorporate the firm under section 659 of the Nigerian Companies and Allied Matters Act (1990).</span>[/rt_tl_event][rt_tl_event month="March," year="2015"]<span style="font-weight: 400;">The Corporate Affairs Commission (CAC) of Nigeria incorporates the firm as a legal entity. DanielHart &amp; Dayo LLP is listed in the CAC’s register of business names, and certified as a “legal practice and consultancy” with the following certification number: BN2337967.</span>[/rt_tl_event][rt_tl_event month="March," year="2015"]<span style="font-weight: 400;">Client enquires are being answered.</span>[/rt_tl_event][/rt_timeline][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row rt_row_background_width="default" rt_row_content_width="default" rt_row_style="alt-style-2" rt_row_paddings="true" rt_bg_effect="classic" rt_bg_parallax_effect="1" rt_bg_image_repeat="repeat" rt_bg_size="cover" rt_bg_position="right top" rt_bg_attachment="scroll" rt_overlap="" rt_padding_top="60" rt_padding_bottom="60" rt_row_borders="" rt_grid=""][vc_column width="1/1"