gy company need a subsidiary in Israel?  Are you interested in banking in Singapore, Switzerland or Luxembourg? Does your energy company desire a presence in the Gulf Markets?</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 100;">Our global coverage goes beyond partner offices in some of the world’s most important cities. The Millennial Lawyers Club acts a network of global law firms who combine our international resources and sector expertise. We can work on cross-border transactions in the markets and regions important to our clients. Each firm also refers its individual clients to other members of the Club—when their clients need representation in a jurisdiction a club member is based. We have one club member per jurisdiction.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 100;">The Millennial Lawyers Club has allowed DanielHart &amp; Dayo LLP to combine our local depth with a global reach that is simply unrivalled in Nigeria.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'OUR  GLOBAL NETWORK', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2724-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-25 22:12:40', '2015-09-25 22:12:40', '', 2724, 'http://www.danielhartdayo.com/2015/09/25/2724-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
