n investment portfolio. This is a short-list of our citizenship portfolio options. We assist you in the choice of the best strategy to meet your particular objectives and turn your vision into reality – based on your convictions, ideals and economic ability.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 100;">To you sustain your corporate citizenship portfolio, we provide information on events, the latest research publications, as well as a network of thematic experts and strategic partner organizations to compliment your business objectives.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Being a Corporate Citizen', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2726-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-10-17 14:01:38', '2015-10-17 14:01:38', '', 2726, 'http://www.danielhartdayo.com/2015/10/17/2726-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
