(2994, 1, '2015-10-20 20:13:43', '2015-10-20 20:13:43', '[vc_row rt_row_background_width="default" rt_row_content_width="fullwidth" rt_row_style="default-style" rt_row_borders="" rt_overlap="" rt_grid="" rt_row_paddings="true" rt_bg_image="2993" rt_bg_effect="classic" rt_bg_parallax_effect="1" rt_bg_image_repeat="repeat" rt_bg_size="cover" rt_bg_position="right top" rt_bg_attachment="scroll" rt_padding_bottom="200" rt_padding_top="200"][vc_column][rt_heading style="style-1" size="h1"][/rt_heading][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row rt_row_background_width="default" rt_row_content_width="default" rt_row_style="default-style" rt_overlap="true" rt_row_paddings="true" rt_bg_effect="classic" rt_bg_parallax_effect="1" rt_bg_image_repeat="repeat" rt_bg_size="cover" rt_bg_position="right top" rt_bg_attachment="scroll" rt_row_borders="bottom" rt_grid="" class="txt-justify"][vc_column width="1/1"][rt_heading style="style-1" size="h1"]Our Global Network[/rt_heading][vc_column_text]<span style="font-weight: 100;">DanielHart &amp; Dayo LLP created the Millennial Lawyers Club and operates as the Club’s headquarters. The Club fulfills our vision to help clients deliver their global strategies. We have built a truly global network of millennial lawyers who own special law firms in strategic markets and fast growing economies.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 100;">We now span every continent—ready to legally represent your interests in attractive markets. Each law firm in our club applies a futuristic mindset to your business objectives. The millennial generation is at the vanguard of the current century. As lawyers, we are best positioned to navigate your interests in an era of connectivity, scrutiny and stakeholder economics. We apply our generation’s values—ambition, creativity, understanding and social responsibility—to your business''s growth plan.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 100;">Do you want to expand your business into Ethiopia, Rwanda or other emerging markets in Africa? Does your technology company need a subsidiary in Israel?  Are you interested in banking in Singapore, Switzerland or Luxembourg? Does your energy company desire a presence in the Gulf Markets?</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 100;">Our global coverage goes beyond partner offices in some of the world’s most important cities. The Millennial Lawyers Club acts a network of global law firms who combine our international resources and sector expertise. We can work on cross-border transactions in the markets and regions important to our clients. Each firm also refers its individual clients to other members of the Club—when their clients need representation in a jurisdiction a club member is based. We have one club member per jurisdiction.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 100;">The Millennial Lawyers Club has allowed DanielHart &amp; Dayo LLP to combine our local depth with a global reach that is simply unrivalled in Nigeria.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'OUR  GLOBAL NETWORK', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2724-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-10-20 20:13:43', '2015-10-20 20:13:43', '', 2724, 'http://www.danielhartdayo.com/2015/10/20/2724-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
