nt opportunities in Ethiopia, Rwanda or in equally promising emerging markets across Africa. You may wish to join the next wave of investors in the technology boom in Israel or in the private equity offerings in Nigeria. Wherever your investment interests may be positioned, we have a network of future-minded lawyers prepared to represent you. We have expertise in financial and corporate laws in Singapore, Switzerland and Luxembourg, as well as expertise in energy laws in the Gulf Markets. We are in the jurisdictions you want to do business in. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 100;">Our global coverage goes beyond partner offices in some of the world’s most exciting cities. We know that being present is just the start. Beyond our global reach, the Millennial Lawyers Club combines the international resources and sector expertise of all member law firms. This means we can also work on cross-border transactions in the markets and regions important to our clients. Each firm also refers its individual clients to other members of the Club—when their clients need representation in another jurisdiction where a club member is based. Accordingly, we have one club member per jurisdiction.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 100;">The Millennial Lawyers Club has allowed DanielHart &amp; Dayo LLP to combine our local depth with a global reach that has special significance among law firms in Nigeria.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'OUR  GLOBAL NETWORK', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2724-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-11-01 22:32:44', '2016-11-01 22:32:44', '', 2724, 'http://www.danielhartdayo.com/2016/11/01/2724-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
